OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782748079
OL,3,CDrug driver jailed after causing fatal
OL,4,Ccrash when 16 times over legal limit
OL,6,FDashcam footage shows Daniel Booth
OL,7,Fswerving and commenting about his
OL,8,Ftiredness in the lead-up to the crash.
OL,9,FPictures from Avon and Somerset Police.
OL,11,FA man has been jailed for a fatal
OL,12,Fcrash he caused when 16 times over the
OL,13,Flegal drug-drive limit.
OL,15,FDaniel Booth was driving in Aust when
OL,16,Fhis car veered into the path of an
OL,17,Foncoming bike, ridden by 56-year-old
OL,18,FNeil Routley, who died from the
OL,19,Finjuries he sustained on 29 June 2025.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782748079
OL,3,CDrug driver jailed after causing fatal
OL,4,Ccrash when 16 times over legal limit
OL,6,FEmergency services were called to Aust
OL,7,FRoad at about 12.30pm and Booth, from
OL,8,FLydney in Gloucestershire, was
OL,9,Farrested at the scene.
OL,11,FHe was found to have 14 micrograms of
OL,12,Fcocaine and 800 micrograms of
OL,13,Fbenzoylecgonine (BZE) in his system.
OL,14,FThe legal limit is 10 micrograms and
OL,15,F50 micrograms respectively.
OL,17,FThe court was told Booth had taken
OL,18,Fcocaine approximately 12 hours before
OL,19,Fthe incident and the delayed impact of
OL,20,Ftaking the drug had impaired his
OL,21,Fdriving.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782748079
OL,3,CDrug driver jailed after causing fatal
OL,4,Ccrash when 16 times over legal limit
OL,6,FThe 31-year-old was driving a Mercedes
OL,7,Fcar at the time of the collision,
OL,8,Fwhich was fitted with a dashcam. The
OL,9,Ffootage was reviewed during our
OL,10,Finvestigation and showed Booth on
OL,11,Fmultiple occasions hitting kerbs and
OL,12,Fverges in the minutes before the
OL,13,Fincident. He also could be heard
OL,14,Fyawning and making a comment about
OL,15,Ffeeling tired.
OL,17,FJo Routley, Daniel's wife, said her
OL,18,Fhusband was "hugely missed by those
OL,19,Fwho knew and loved him".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782748079
OL,3,CDrug driver jailed after causing fatal
OL,4,Ccrash when 16 times over legal limit
OL,6,FShe said: "Neil was a much-loved
OL,7,Fhusband, brother and son. We are
OL,8,Fdevastated by his loss.
OL,10,F"After 20 years teaching maths, Neil
OL,11,Fleft Patchway High School to fulfil
OL,12,Fhis dream of working for himself as a
OL,13,Fcycle mechanic, though he continued
OL,14,Fhis love of teaching by helping his
OL,15,Fcustomers and instructing at archery.
OL,17,F"He was always active, enjoying
OL,18,Fparagliding, paddleboarding, badminton
OL,19,Fand rifle shooting. His main passions
OL,20,Fwere cats, coffee and cycling.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782748079
OL,3,CDrug driver jailed after causing fatal
OL,4,Ccrash when 16 times over legal limit
OL,6,F"Sunday 29 June last year was a hot
OL,7,Fday, like today, so Neil went for a
OL,8,Fmorning cycle when it was cooler.
OL,10,F"He was due to be back for lunch so we
OL,11,Fcould go for a walk together in the
OL,12,Fafternoon. Tragically, he never came
OL,13,Fhome.
OL,15,F"Neil's untimely death was caused by a
OL,16,Fselfish and thoughtless act, which
OL,17,Fwill continue to impact his family and
OL,18,Ffriends every day.
OL,20,F"His family and friends will miss him
OL,21,Fgreatly."
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782748079
OL,3,CDrug driver jailed after causing fatal
OL,4,Ccrash when 16 times over legal limit
OL,6,FBooth pleaded guilty at Bristol Crown
OL,7,FCourt at a previous hearing to causing
OL,8,Fdeath by dangerous driving and was
OL,9,Fsentenced on Thursday 25 June. He had
OL,10,Fno previous convictions.
OL,12,FJudge Martin Picton accepted Booth was
OL,13,Fremorseful, but explained Booth knew
OL,14,Fthe risk he was taking.
OL,16,FHe added: "The dangers of drug-driving
OL,17,Fare well known.. No-one can be
OL,18,Fignorant of the risk. The message is
OL,19,Fout there, that drug-driving kills."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782748079
OL,3,CDrug driver jailed after causing fatal
OL,4,Ccrash when 16 times over legal limit
OL,6,FBooth received a prison sentence of
OL,7,Fnine years. He was also disqualified
OL,8,Ffrom driving for five years and will
OL,9,Fhave to pass an extended test before
OL,10,Fbeing allowed to regain his licence.
OL,12,FDesignated Investigating Officer Emma
OL,13,FLing said: "This incident has
OL,14,Fdevastated Neil Routley's family and
OL,15,Four thoughts are with them. It's clear
OL,16,Fhis death has left a massive hole in
OL,17,Ftheir lives that no court sentence
OL,18,Fcould ever fill.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782748079
OL,3,CDrug driver jailed after causing fatal
OL,4,Ccrash when 16 times over legal limit
OL,6,F"There are times when accidents can
OL,7,Fhappen and there is nothing anyone
OL,8,Fcould have done about them. However,
OL,9,Fthis is not the case with this tragedy.
OL,11,F"Daniel Booth got behind the wheel
OL,12,Fthat day and was clearly in no safe
OL,13,Fcondition to drive. The dashcam
OL,14,Ffootage showing his car striking kerb
OL,15,Fmultiple times and capturing him
OL,16,Fyawning is truly shocking. Yet he
OL,17,Fcontinued to drive on.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782748079
OL,3,CDrug driver jailed after causing fatal
OL,4,Ccrash when 16 times over legal limit
OL,6,F"Driving after consuming drugs or
OL,7,Falcohol massively increases the chance
OL,8,Fof a serious collision, even if it is
OL,9,Fseveral hours later. Driving under the
OL,10,Finfluence is recognised as one of the
OL,11,Ffatal five most common reasons behind
OL,12,Fsuch incidents.
OL,14,F"We make no apology for highlighting
OL,15,Fthis repeatedly because the
OL,16,Fconsequences of drivers ignoring that
OL,17,Fdanger is devastating, as has been
OL,18,Fsadly illustrated in this case."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782748079
OL,3,CDrug driver jailed after causing fatal
OL,4,Ccrash when 16 times over legal limit
OL,6,FSenior Crown Advocate, Christine Hart,
OL,7,Fsaid: "The sentence today follows a
OL,8,Fthorough police investigation and
OL,9,Fclose partnership working with the CPS
OL,10,Fto put together a strong case with
OL,11,Fevidence so compelling it left Mr
OL,12,FBooth with no choice but to plead
OL,13,Fguilty.
OL,15,F"I'd like to thank the Mr Routley's
OL,16,Ffamily for their patience and dignity
OL,17,Fthroughout these proceedings."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
